practice daily
starts with easy problem(for begineer)
break big problem into smaller sub problem
think firstly about brute->best/optimized(use bramashtra for optimization if needed)
watch editorials/solutions after stuck for long time(or not stuck bcz of better knowledge)
make notes of every problem
firstly try to code yourself(for some time)
upload the solution in github
mention the comments with code in your own language
take daily own target to solve problems(2-3 min)
revise the problem daily before sleeping at night
revise with weekly plans(on weekend for remind)
make the dry run of every problem after do it
also think about edges cases(selfly)--> means where the code breaks/wrong
time and space complexity of every problem
constraints ko bhi dekho every problem ke bcz isse kafi idea lagta h data structure ka...aur time comp. ka
pattern recognition after/during every problme (and note it down)
Explain out loud--> like in interview (“main yahan hashmap use kar raha because lookup O(1)”)


